The surveys,

52:25.533 --> 52:27.970
making the drill pad,

52:28.188 --> 52:29.711
moving the gear,
housing the crew,

52:29.929 --> 52:31.191
setting the drill,
capping the well,

52:31.365 --> 52:32.801
