52:50.776 --> 52:52.299
I need a favor.

52:52.473 --> 52:53.953
Will you do me a favor?

52:54.127 --> 52:55.433
Depends on what the favor is.

52:57.086 --> 52:58.958
Put me on another crew.

53:00.742 --> 53:02.179
You know, a lot of people
are gonna blame you

53:02.309 --> 53:04.311
for what happened.

53:04.485 --> 53:06.661
Anytime something goes wrong,
they always blame the worm.

53:06.835 --> 53:08.489
Let me.

53:13.102 --> 53:14.800
All right, I'll find you a crew.

53:16.584 --> 53:18.456
<i>♪ So, I don't know... ♪</i>

53:18.630 --> 53:20.371
Listen, your sister's in town.

53:20.588 --> 53:21.807
You want to run
by the house and see her?

53:22.024 --> 53:23.330
