back up my dick.

53:25.158 --> 53:27.378
Fair enough.

53:29.597 --> 53:31.425
You want to go by the café
and get a beer?

53:32.687 --> 53:33.819
It's eight in the morning.

53:33.949 --> 53:35.603
It's Sunday.

53:35.777 --> 53:37.083
What else you got to do?

53:37.257 --> 53:39.520
[chuckles]
Why not?

53:39.694 --> 53:41.435
All right.

